# The frozen v2 engine and the v2 test copies are never linted (v2-src is a
# record mined by the Phase-15 converter; test/V2 must stay byte-identical;
# test/v2-working holds v2-syntax migration source, not v3 code).
# test/__mocks__ is v2-only HTTP mock infrastructure used by `yarn test:v2`;
# v3 tests use the injected MockHttpClient double (test/helpers) instead.
